                                                <h1
                                                        class="text-dark text-700 font-size-33 text-hover-inverse-white fw-bolder">
                                                    <a href="https://hegka.com/articles/thu-ky-lam-gi-mo-ta-cong-viec-muc-luong-vi-tri-thu-ky">
                                                        Thư ký làm gì? Mô tả công việc, mức lương vị trí Thư ký?
                                                    </a>
                                                </h1>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="ads-background">
                                                <a class="symbol symbol-35px symbol-circle pb-6 pt-5 w-100"
                                                   href="https://hegka.com/koc/chungngo">
                                                    <img src="https://hegka.com/storage/profile-photos/ztdynhz1TEB6ebVu3uyj29La8sB3gaXPgTBN2aMY.jpg"
